line_2: Yet vainly wou'd despotick will conclude,

line_1: And view composed this silent multitude: —
line_2: Now bid thy soul man's busy scenes exclude,

line_1: And teach the great to spurn the multitude.
line_2: Far hence the tribe, whose servile arts delude,

line_1: In motley dress, a sparkling multitude.
line_2: Within, a group of female figures stood,

line_1: Yet always culls amidst the Multitude
line_2: Such as are very dull, or very lewd.
